h3 User
p User: #{@user.name}
p Email: #{@user.email if @user.email}

h4 Achievements
- @user.achievements.each do |achievement|
  = link_to image_tag(achievement.badge.image.url, :class => "img-circle"), achievement, :method => :delete, :confirm => "Are you sure you want to remove the #{achievement.badge.name} badge?"

h4 Available Achievements
- @unearned_badges.each do |badge|
  = link_to image_tag(badge.image.url, :class => "img-circle"), new_achievement_path(@user, badge), :method => :post
